Title: Episode #1.1
Writer: Charles S. Forsman (based on the comic book by), Charlie Covell, Jonathan Entwistle (created by)

Plot: Alyssa is teen angst personified. She feels estranged from her mother, hates her stepfather and rejects pretty much everyone she meets - until one day she sees James sitting alone.
